Paste This Dependency In Your pubspec.yaml file

maps_launcher: ^2.0.0

run Pub get 

Then Paste This Code In any Of your Button

 onPressed: () {
                  MapsLauncher.launchQuery ('Nexskill, Punjab, Pakistan'); // Change Text According To Your Need  

                  MapsLauncher.launchCoordinates(
                     31.53117421411779, 74.33593858177971);     // change longitude and latitude according to your Location
                },
                
